The stress this girl goes thru.....the whole performance should be on YouTubebut i clicked the link cuz i missed her performance. Ari is doing a great job of working hard and using her pain in life to create amazing music....her snub was a get back from last year. I know she only performed for her fans and no one else.
She is the queen of making lemonade from lemons at this point. Broke my heart tho to see her fighting back tears and breaking down at the end of the performance. Ari is not ok....that girl is internally broken but she keeps it together despite an obvious depression. She really deserved that album of the year grammy but there's no denying her greatness to us. We love you Ari.
